items.title: Vision
items.description: When I say the word 'beauty', what do you envision? ⁠This magnificent abstract painting feels new everytime you look at it.⁠ With loads of different colors, long brushstrokes and subtle details, this painting never gets boring!⁠

items.title: Flower
items.description: Designed to resonate & spark a mix of feelings. Every day. Whether you love art or just looking to decorate, this handmade painting will instantly create a new ambience in your home or office.
